    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/e280d38e3d44fa457c14efc3e971eea6.poster.avif?t=1759762627\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/e280d38e3d44fa457c14efc3e971eea6.webm?t=1759762627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/e280d38e3d44fa457c14efc3e971eea6.mp4?t=1759762627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫步在风景如画的森林中，远离城市的喧嚣。享受大自然，采摘蘑菇，沉浸在宁静的氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >森林小径隐藏着许多秘密。探索每个角落，寻找稀有的蘑菇品种，成为真正的真菌学鉴赏家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/2b3f255052bcd451d2daf3564e0ee242.poster.avif?t=1759762627\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/2b3f255052bcd451d2daf3564e0ee242.webm?t=1759762627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262810/extras/2b3f255052bcd451d2daf3564e0ee242.mp4?t=1759762627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索七个不同的地点，了解它们独特的地方和植被、不同的天气和采摘蘑菇的条件。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有 32 种流行的蘑菇，它们都有自己的生长区域。每种蘑菇都有几个生长阶段，有自己独特的质量等级和重量。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成各种任务。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的篮子和刀，收集更多的蘑菇，获得更多的经验和硬币。</p></li></ul>",
